CRM Web Application
Technologies: Python, Django, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PostgreSQL
Role: Full Stack Developer
Duration: Jan 2025 â€“ Mar 2025

Description:
Developed a web-based Customer Relationship Management (CRM) system to manage leads, customers, follow-ups, and sales activities. Implemented role-based access for Admin, Sales, and Support teams.

Key Features:

User Login, Signup, and Role-based Access (Admin, Sales, Support)

Lead Management (Add, Update, Track, Assign leads)

Customer Details and Interaction History

Task & Follow-up Reminders

Sales Dashboard with charts and statistics

Export reports in CSV format

Admin Panel to manage users and settings
